# Output Contracts 

Use structured outputs for:

- bug analysis;
- root cause;
- impact analysis;
- correction proposal;
- code review;
- SQL review;
- fiscal validation;
- test generation;
- refactoring;
- troubleshooting;
- debugging.

Every technical conclusion must include:

- evidence;
- facts vs inferences vs hypotheses;
- risk;
- validation;
- confidence;
- human approval requirement;
- pending questions.

